<br>
I want it moved from body because everyone gets max body, and some people don't have max energy or heat, especially classes that have to get +skill to several spec lines.  It is certainly true that the majority of our enemies have decent resists to all tables.  but some classes will not, they will have to make sacrafices.<br>
<br>
I also  have noticed that some classes, even before sc were really hard to land shouts on.  Take scouts for instance.  They average 70% resist rate to my shouts.  That really really sways the fight in their favor with the shield stun they dish.<br>
<br>
And then you have the variety issue, why are the majority of mid spells in several small resist lines (tho this has changed some with the advent of the BD and the cave shammy)<br>
<br>
But look at resist tables that the enemy has to fear...body. some energy from RC runies, cold and matter (mostly from dot proc weapons)<br>
<br>
No heat.   a little spirit from the 12 Sms running around.<br>
Variety makes things better.  <br>
